{"tid":487070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"膝頭屈到一半會有嘢kick住好痛","createTime":"2017-12-02T12:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T04:13:55.000Z","uid":48405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e3c27f46f8a183402932ce41c377816469555f","tid":487070,"uid":48405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲試過屈膝屈到一半會好似有條根kick住屈唔落咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係有時申翻直 或者卒兩卒 又會無事正常翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係咩事 因為其實都好耐嘅事 所以有時一係就忍住痛 一下快趣落到底 啪一聲痛嘅 一係就申翻直 卒下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係最搞鬼係唔一定卒完申完就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f1de74d1281f284df6e860634c1f812505da13","tid":487070,"uid":48405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"我諗緊睇鐵打定西醫好 成日覺得西醫hea鳩鳩就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10cce3c16274f553d5a1fac2e7b7807ecdee78f","tid":487070,"uid":79363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況不論睇中醫西醫都好，最好檢查清楚先。<br />\n唔知之前病史，就咁睇唔排除有半月板撕裂情況，唔好亂咁啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申中醫"},{"pid":"1128b0c6c93344a47964f3114cf7f8a65dfd0c92","tid":487070,"uid":8460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:13:42.000Z","msg":"如果情況出現左一段時間<br />\n好大機會係&rdquo;locking&rdquo;<br />\n半月板有少少部分碎左kick住<br />\n睇西醫或者物理治療照照佢穩陣，仲有得救<br />\n等到grade III就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc2d6b01c5da14cc837a727a5ae3c5129ba6ecb","tid":487070,"uid":147789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"做掌上掌個陣左手手肘會kick 住kick 住<br />\n每次都因為種感覺太唔舒服而做唔落去"},{"pi