aces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁突然碎左？但係我正常打波 跑步 跳起都無問題 唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔住個moon答你唔到，所以先話要檢查，最起碼都要見到隻腳做測試啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34edfe08cdd65927aeee172cd94f16395790ce8c","tid":487070,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T13:11:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc1d3b34d86b9bf283e5cd0d256332bd0a8983a9","tid":487070,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做掌上掌個陣左手手肘會kick 住kick 住<br />\n每次都因為種感覺太唔舒服而做唔落去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMedial/Lateral epicondylitis? 有冇成日做離心收縮既動作，舉鐵練二頭肌，打羽毛/網球個d</blockquote><br />\n冇喎 會唔會出事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}